00:01:59.256 --> 00:02:00.897
When I count to three,

00:02:01.336 --> 00:02:03.176
I'll make my move.

00:02:05.496 --> 00:02:06.736
Three...

00:02:09.416 --> 00:02:11.057
You really are calculating

00:02:11.297 --> 00:02:12.497
and good at biding your time.

00:02:12.856 --> 00:02:14.737
Your first attempt
with the Yang poison failed.

00:02:14.897 --> 00:02:15.655
The second time,

00:02:15.656 --> 00:02:17.577
you used my bond with Chu Moshang

00:02:17.816 --> 00:02:19.337
to lure him back to me
from the sanctuary,

00:02:19.376 --> 00:02:21.176
even after he lost his dragon pearl.

00:02:21.177 --> 00:02:23.816
You think you can lecture me
like a sister-in-law.

00:02:24.017 --> 00:02:25.016
Even your tone

00:02:25.017 --> 00:02:27.096
sounds like Moshang now.

00:02:32.417 --> 00:02:34.096
You went to all this trouble

00:02:34.177 --> 00:02:35.736
just to use this chance
to get rid of me,

00:02:35.737 --> 00:02:36.816
didn't you?

00:02:38.096 --> 00:02:39.136
Yes.

00:02:39.376 --> 00:02:40.816
As long as you're alive,

00:02:41.376 --> 00:02:44.256
I'll always be Father's second choice.

00:02:44.496 --> 00:02:45.816
As for her,

00:02:45.977 --> 00:02:47.416
she can't live either.

00:02:47.737 --> 00:02:50.376
She actually carries
the bloodline of the Dragons.

00:02:53.417 --> 00:02:56.057
Looks like I have another
mess to clean up.

00:02:57.816 --> 00:03:00.096
Take the heart-guard scale
to the Chu residence.

00:03:00.177 --> 00:03:01.337
I'll come for you.

00:03:01.737 --> 00:03:02.897
Be careful.

00:03:03.216 --> 00:03:04.577
Promise me you'll come back to me.

00:03:10.656 --> 00:03:11.976
Chu Moshang,

00:03:12.616 --> 00:03:15.096
I think love has made you
lose your mind.

00:03:15.457 --> 00:03:17.870
You actually risked your life
pulling out your heart-guard scale.

00:03:17.870 --> 00:03:19.096
You're dead today.

00:04:05.656 --> 00:04:06.856
Why are you standing out here?

00:04:06.977 --> 00:04:08.177
You're pregnant.

00:04:08.376 --> 00:04:09.095
Come on.

00:04:09.096 --> 00:04:10.017
Let's go inside.

00:04:20.616 --> 00:04:21.495
I had someone

00:04:21.496 --> 00:04:23.017
bring these pastries back from Wujing.

00:04:23.137 --> 00:04:24.137
Have something sweet.

00:04:24.336 --> 00:04:25.536
It'll take the bitterness away.

00:04:35.976 --> 00:04:36.897
It really is sweet.

00:04:39.697 --> 00:04:41.536
Ever since I met you,

00:04:41.937 --> 00:04:43.616
you've always been a handful.

00:04:44.216 --> 00:04:45.535
You find trouble everywhere.

00:04:45.536 --> 00:04:47.817
You're stubborn,
and you rub people the wrong way.

00:04:48.497 --> 00:04:49.937
Don't blame Father.

00:04:50.736 --> 00:04:52.257
He really had no choice.

00:04:55.497 --> 00:04:57.017
Marrying someone like me

00:04:58.057 --> 00:04:59.457
has been such a burden on you.

00:05:01.377 --> 00:05:03.777
I made you suffer at home.

00:05:05.017 --> 00:05:06.017
I'm sorry.

00:05:06.096 --> 00:05:08.017
At least I helped you
find your spiritual root

00:05:08.096 --> 00:05:09.217
so you can cultivate.

00:05:09.897 --> 00:05:11.137
You're intelligent.

00:05:11.377 --> 00:05:12.616
You hate following the rules.

00:05:13.137 --> 00:05:14.817
You learn the hard way.

00:05:14.976 --> 00:05:16.096
You've become more composed

00:05:16.257 --> 00:05:17.457
when handling things.

00:05:25.377 --> 00:05:26.457
Chu Moshang,

00:05:26.697 --> 00:05:29.096
I know something happened to you.

00:05:29.137 --> 00:05:29.856
But,

00:05:30.937 --> 00:05:32.697
don't leave me behind, okay?

00:05:33.497 --> 00:05:34.377
We...

00:05:35.176 --> 00:05:37.017
We and the child still have a future,

00:05:37.497 --> 00:05:38.137
right?

00:05:38.416 --> 00:05:39.697
When this is all over,

00:05:40.096 --> 00:05:41.416
Father will understand

00:05:41.697 --> 00:05:43.056
why I chose to marry you.

00:05:43.096 --> 00:05:44.176
As for our child,

00:05:44.817 --> 00:05:45.897
if he's like you,

00:05:46.176 --> 00:05:47.496
I'll have nothing to worry about.

00:05:47.937 --> 00:05:49.056
We'll just have to teach him

00:05:49.176 --> 00:05:50.656
not to be as uptight as me.

00:05:51.457 --> 00:05:52.856
That's exhausting.

00:06:06.656 --> 00:06:07.616
Chu Moshang,

00:06:10.296 --> 00:06:12.257
I don't like what you're saying.

00:06:13.057 --> 00:06:14.137
Tell me.

00:06:14.457 --> 00:06:16.736
Did you already get rid of Nie Rongzhi?

00:06:25.216 --> 00:06:26.296
I know.

00:06:26.577 --> 00:06:28.056
I'm still dreaming right now.

00:06:28.377 --> 00:06:29.377
Chu Moshang,

00:06:29.497 --> 00:06:31.257
if you lose the dragon pearl,

00:06:31.697 --> 00:06:33.616
you'll be at Nie Rongzhi's mercy.

00:06:33.617 --> 00:06:35.496
Once he becomes the Dragon King,

00:06:35.697 --> 00:06:37.855
he'll never let you survive.

00:06:37.856 --> 00:06:38.976
If that's how it ends,

00:06:39.497 --> 00:06:41.056
it means I wasn't strong enough.

00:06:41.377 --> 00:06:42.777
It has nothing to do with you.

00:06:43.096 --> 00:06:43.937
Zhilou,

00:06:44.497 --> 00:06:45.656
our duty

00:06:45.776 --> 00:06:47.817
was never to become
Dragon King and Queen.

00:06:48.057 --> 00:06:50.056
We have something more important to do.

00:06:56.176 --> 00:06:57.096
I know.

00:06:57.536 --> 00:06:59.536
We've always understood each other.

00:07:00.216 --> 00:07:01.496
Before I came here,

00:07:01.697 --> 00:07:03.536
I told Hunbao the same thing.

00:07:03.736 --> 00:07:05.017
You want to protect your family

00:07:05.457 --> 00:07:06.697
and Feng Manor,

00:07:07.296 --> 00:07:09.176
but you don't have to become
the Wujing Saintess.

00:07:09.536 --> 00:07:10.936
I want to protect the sanctuary,

00:07:10.937 --> 00:07:12.817
but I don't have to be Dragon King.

00:07:13.257 --> 00:07:15.897
I'm a Dragon God
with thousands of years' lifespan.

00:07:16.137 --> 00:07:18.056
I feel deeply
for every part of this world

00:07:18.057 --> 00:07:19.536
and every living being in it.

00:07:20.017 --> 00:07:22.056
Protecting everything I cherish

00:07:22.577 --> 00:07:24.296
is what I've been doing all along.

00:07:24.536 --> 00:07:25.616
But I'll

00:07:25.937 --> 00:07:27.217
make your path

00:07:27.377 --> 00:07:28.897
harder than it should be.

00:07:31.697 --> 00:07:32.616
Zhilou,

00:07:32.937 --> 00:07:34.257
you saved my life.

00:07:35.057 --> 00:07:36.096
Without you,

00:07:36.497 --> 00:07:38.175
the Yang poison would have killed me.

00:07:38.176 --> 00:07:39.616
I wouldn't have survived.

00:07:39.976 --> 00:07:41.217
But marrying you

00:07:41.577 --> 00:07:42.736
was never about repayment.

00:07:43.617 --> 00:07:44.736
It was duty.

00:07:45.257 --> 00:07:46.817
It was love that found me
before I noticed.

00:07:47.497 --> 00:07:48.656
It was instinct.

00:07:49.577 --> 00:07:51.017
It was a natural pull toward you.

00:08:05.697 --> 00:08:07.176
How is Zhilou doing?

00:08:07.257 --> 00:08:08.496
Hunbao, come with me right now.

00:08:08.497 --> 00:08:10.457
Something happened to Prince Shang
and Feng Zhilou.

00:08:11.257 --> 00:08:11.976
Let's go.

00:08:18.176 --> 00:08:19.056
I'm sorry.

00:08:19.057 --> 00:08:21.056
You'll have to go on alone,

00:08:21.697 --> 00:08:23.377
but my heart-guard scale

00:08:23.897 --> 00:08:25.656
will always protect you.

00:08:27.656 --> 00:08:28.577
No.

00:08:30.656 --> 00:08:31.976
I don't want to be alone.

00:08:32.057 --> 00:08:33.176
Miss Zhilou.

00:08:33.776 --> 00:08:34.937
Miss Zhilou.

00:08:35.416 --> 00:08:36.897
Miss Zhilou, please wake up.

00:08:37.017 --> 00:08:37.976
Miss Zhilou.

00:08:39.217 --> 00:08:40.417
Miss Zhilou.

00:08:43.296 --> 00:08:44.856
What happened?

00:08:45.296 --> 00:08:46.657
What's wrong with me?

00:08:47.217 --> 00:08:48.457
Where's Chu Moshang?

00:08:48.536 --> 00:08:50.217
You passed out at the main gate.

00:08:50.536 --> 00:08:52.537
We brought you here.

00:08:53.377 --> 00:08:54.697
Miss Zhilou,

00:08:54.776 --> 00:08:55.976
